@startuml AWS
title AWS Deployment Proposal

skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

actor User

cloud "AWS" {
  component "App Runner\nAPI Gateway" as APIGW
  component "App Runner\nProducts Service" as PRODUCTS
  component "App Runner\nOrders Service" as ORDERS

  cloud "Amazon ECR" as ECR

  frame "VPC" {
    component "App Runner\nVPC Connector" as VPC_CONN
    database "Amazon RDS\nPostgreSQL" as RDS
  }
}

User --> APIGW : HTTPS
APIGW --> PRODUCTS : HTTP
APIGW --> ORDERS : HTTP
ORDERS --> PRODUCTS : HTTP

APIGW ..> ECR : container image
PRODUCTS ..> ECR : container image
ORDERS ..> ECR : container image

PRODUCTS --> VPC_CONN
ORDERS --> VPC_CONN
VPC_CONN --> RDS : PostgreSQL

note right of RDS
Private database access
through VPC connectivity
end note

@enduml
